Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:20.25,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hey, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:20.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.77,0:00:27.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いね　先生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.45,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Sorry, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You're calling a cat Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.24,0:00:31.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,先生？　猫がか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:33.96,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Doesn't he look wise?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,賢そうな顔してるじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.90,0:00:36.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お客が来ればちゃんと席譲るし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:36.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He gives up his seat when \NI have guests, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.42,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Anyway, you have to hear this, Odasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:39.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それより　聞いてよ　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.75,0:00:42.47,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There was a shootout today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:42.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日ね　銃撃戦があったのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:43.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:46.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,機銃付き幌車で武装した元気な集団と
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.39,0:00:45.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I was trading shots in a warehouse block
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.18,0:00:48.64,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,with an energetic crew armed with \Na machine-gun equipped truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:48.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,倉庫街で撃ち合いになった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:51.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,That's quite the weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:51.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それは随分な装備だな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:55.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,で　お前のその増えた怪我は…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,And what's with your new injuries?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.25,0:00:58.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,銃撃戦の結果　負ったものか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:58.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Is that from this shootout?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.04,0:01:01.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,200,0,0,,その途中でトイレに行きたくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.06,0:01:01.88,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I had to go pee in the midst of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.14,0:01:04.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,then I tripped on a ditch \Nbecause I was in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:04.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,200,0,0,,急いだら排水溝で転んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.18,0:01:06.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.61,0:01:08.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,When you rush, it's hard to avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.73,0:01:08.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,急いでいたなら仕方ないな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.09,0:01:10.71,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:10.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,仕方ないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.51,0:01:13.95,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,His name is Dazai Osamu...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:13.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の名は太宰治
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.32,0:01:17.18,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,An executive in the Port Mafia, \Na criminal organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.44,0:01:17.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,犯罪組織ポートマフィアの幹部だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:19.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,By the way, as for the other guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:22.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ちなみにそいつらは罠を張って軽く小突いたら　泣いて逃げていったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:22.42,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,they ran away crying after I set a \Ntrap and roughed them up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:25.67,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They're a pretty sorry bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.94,0:01:25.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,五円玉のようにパッとしない連中さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.89,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Thanks to them, yet again\N I couldn't manage to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:27.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おかげでまた死にそびれた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:30.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアにはこういう言葉がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.49,0:01:31.05,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,There's a saying among the Port Mafia...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:34.06,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,The biggest misfortune for Dazai's enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.67,0:01:35.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰の敵にとって一番の不幸は　太宰の敵であることだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.11,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,is that they are {\i0}Dazai's {\i1}enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.84,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,His list of deeds writ in darkness and blood
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.99,0:01:42.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が打ち立てた闇と血の一覧を見れば　マフィア内の人間も震え上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.31,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,is enough to make even those \Nin the Mafia tremble.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.70,0:01:45.75,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He was practically born to be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:45.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,マフィアになる為に生まれてきたような男だ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.02,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:51.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あーもう　どこかに簡単で安心な自殺方法はないものかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.02,0:01:51.88,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I wonder if there is a simple, reliable \Nway to commit suicide somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.77,0:01:52.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:52.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:54.32,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:54.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.97,0:01:59.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Man fears death and yet, at the \Nsame time, man is drawn to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.99,0:01:59.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人は死を恐れ　そして同時に死に惹きつけられる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:05.72,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Death is endlessly consumed by \Nmen in cities and in literature.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:05.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,街で　文学の中で　死は繰り返され消費されていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.57,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It is a singular event in one's \Nlife that none may reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:09.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何者にも変換不能な一回限りの死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:12.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That is what I desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.53,0:02:12.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それが私の望みだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:17.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,というわけでマスター　洗剤を一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:17.46,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So on that note, barkeep, can \NI have a cup of detergent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.39,0:02:18.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:18.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Bar,0,0,0,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.58,0:02:19.96,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.61,0:02:19.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.83,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Then how about a detergent-based cocktail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.82,0:02:22.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあ洗剤ベースのカクテルを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:24.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Bar,0,0,0,,We don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:26.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I guess there's nothing \Nyou can do about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ないものは仕方ないな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作さん　それ突っ込む処ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:29.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Odasaku-san, you should've called him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:34.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,It's because you never do \Nthat Dazai-kun goes off the rails.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.24,0:02:34.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが突っ込みを疎かにするから　太宰君が暴走するんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.42,0:02:35.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.49,0:02:35.41,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Ango!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,金槌で後頭部に突っ込むくらいが丁度いいんです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:39.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,You should call him out with just about the \Nforce of a hammer hitting the back of his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I'm driving today, so tomato juice, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:42.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今日は車なので　トマトジュースを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:43.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:45.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,暫くぶりだね　仕事帰りかい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.13,0:02:45.21,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Are you on your way back from a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,非道い一日でした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.61,0:02:47.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,It was a bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:50.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,It took way too much time \Nto buy smuggled items.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:50.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,密輸品の買い付けに手間取りましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:52.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,After haggling until eight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,八時まで粘って　成果はこの骨董時計一つですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:54.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,all I have to show for my \Nefforts is this antique watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:59.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}This concludes about 74% \Nof transactions for this quarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:58.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これで今四半期取引のうち　７４％…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:03:00.54,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,His name is Sakaguchi Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.31,0:03:00.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の名は坂口安吾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:03.98,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,取引前例のない組織が８％であることを加味すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}If I account for the 8% \Nof existing organizations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.29,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He is one of the Port Mafia's \Nintelligence officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:03.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィア所属の情報員だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}with which we've never had \Nany transactions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:06.50,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Almost all critical and \Nclassified information
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.95,0:03:09.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}our profit has exceeded \Nlast year's by 34%.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:09.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,重要で機密性の高い情報はほとんど安吾を介して外部とやり取りされる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.50,0:03:09.40,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,pass through Ango when\N communicating with outsiders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:11.91,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,これも史上最年少幹部のご利益ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:12.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}Perhaps it is thanks to our youngest \Nexecutive in the organization's history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:14.80,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,His head's full of information about the \NPort Mafia that's more valuable than gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:14.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の頭の中には黄金よりも貴重なマフィアの情報が詰まっていて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.37,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃどうも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.22,0:03:13.32,Stray Dogs - Default,{\an8}D,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:18.58,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,当然　今日の散々な取引も含むということになりますね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:18.68,Stray Dogs - Default,{\an8}Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}Of course, this summation includes \Ntoday's disastrous deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:18.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,拷問してでも吐かせたい敵組織は星の数ほどいる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.32,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,There must be as many enemy organizations \Nas there are stars in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.32,0:03:18.71,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,who wish to torture him for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:21.47,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,It's a job that requires considerable grit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.98,0:03:21.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,相当な頑丈さが求められる仕事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So Ango fuzzed his job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.92,0:03:24.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾も仕事でしゅっぱいしたってことか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:26.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,"Fuzzed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:25.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,しゅっぱい？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.99,0:03:28.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そう　しゅっぱい仲間だ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Yeah, we're fuzz buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:32.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そういえば私達がここでこうやって飲むようになって随分経つけど
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:32.35,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it's been a long time \Nsince we first became drinking buddies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:35.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作の仕事の愚痴は聞いたことがない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.90,0:03:35.80,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But I've never heard you \Ncomplain about work, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:40.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のような最下級構成員の仕事内容を聞いても退屈なだけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It'd only bore you to hear my stories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,as the lowest-ranking member \Nof the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.03,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,There you go being secretive again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:43.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,またそうやって隠す
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.27,0:03:44.74,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,What'd you do this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:44.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今回はどんなことをした
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.04,0:03:47.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I punished a kid stealing from a store
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:50.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちに上納金を納めてる商店街で子どもが万引きしていたのを懲らしめた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:50.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,in a shopping district that\N pays us protection money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.61,0:03:53.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I mediated a tense face-off between \Nthe lover and the wife of one of our
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,フロント企業の役員が愛人と妻に挟まれた修羅場で仲裁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,shell company executives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:59.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Lastly, I disposed of a dud that was found \Nbehind one of the Mafia offices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:59.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あとはマフィア事務所の裏手で見つかった不発弾の処理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.45,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hey, Odasaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:02.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　織田作　私と仕事を交換しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.45,0:04:02.34,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Let's change jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.49,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I want to dispose of duds, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.35,0:04:04.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私も不発弾の処理やりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:06.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be able to handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:06.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰君には無理です
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:07.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah, you'd get blown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:07.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　吹っ飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.93,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Blown up?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:08.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,吹っ飛ぶ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear that, Ango?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　聞いた　安吾　吹っ飛ぶって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He said blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.00,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'd get blown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私吹っ飛ぶって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:16.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のような最下級構成員の処へ転がり込んでくる仕事は
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.83,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,The kind of jobs that come my \Nway as the lowest-ranking member
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:14.45,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,私どのくらい吹っ飛ぶ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.49,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,{\an8} How far will I get blown away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.54,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,知りません
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:15.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.91,0:04:19.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,{\an8}If you'd like, I can blow you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.27,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,お望みなら　僕が吹っ飛ばして差し上げましょうか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:19.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,are all crap jobs no one\N wants to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:19.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誰もやりたがらない溝浚いばかり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,{\an8} You'd do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.75,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,マジでー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:22.89,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Basically, I'm the organization's handyman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,要するに　組織の何でも屋といったところだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:28.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ところで　今日お二人がこの店にいたのは何かの会合ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:28.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,are the two of you here today for a meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:31.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai just happened to be \Nhere when I walked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:31.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに来たら太宰がいただけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I just had a feeling I'd run into you two
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:35.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今夜ここに来たら　君達に会えるような気がしてね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.90,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,if I came here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Did you need something from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕達に用事があったのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.16,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:40.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,別にないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:41.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I just thought
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:41.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:46.65,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,tonight might become the \Nusual night if I did come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:46.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうしたらいつもの夜になるかなと思っただけさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:48.44,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.43,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,What are we toasting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何に乾杯するんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.72,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Anything's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.69,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何でもいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:57.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I don't really need a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:57.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,理由が欲しいわけじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,To the stray dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.97,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ストレイドッグに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.48,0:05:08.95,Stray Dogs - Default,DA,0,0,0,,To the stray dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ストレイドッグに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.75,0:05:15.57,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hey, Ango, do you have a camera \Nin your bag by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:15.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　安吾　その鞄の中に写真機あった？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:18.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,Yeah, though it's for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:18.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　仕事用ですが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,写真撮ろうよ　記念にさ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:21.10,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Let's take a photo to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:22.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,記念？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:22.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,To remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:23.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.33,0:05:23.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何の記念だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:27.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That the three of us were gathered here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:27.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ここに三人が集まった記念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:29.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,But the three of us are \Nalways drinking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いつも三人で飲んでるじゃないか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,As the executive wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.50,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,幹部殿の仰せのままに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:35.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Make sure you take a good photo of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,かっこよく撮ってよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.95,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Taking it from this angle \Nmakes me look more manly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,このアングルが男前に撮れる
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:41.02,sign_8114_134_Dazai_Osamu_,Sign 0541,0,0,0,,Dazai Osamu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:41.02,sign_8114_133_Ability___No_Lon,Sign 0541,0,0,0,,Ability: \NNo Longer \NHuman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.73,sign_8180_136_Sakaguchi__Ango_,Sign 0542,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi \NAngo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Ango,0,0,0,,I don't need {\i1}my{\i0} photo taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕はいいですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.73,sign_8180_137_Ability__Discour,Sign 0542,0,0,0,,Ability: Discourse\Non Decadence
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.45,sign_8245_138_Oda__Sakunosuke,Sign 0545,0,0,0,,Oda \NSakunosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.45,sign_8275_138_Ability___Flawle,Sign 0545,0,0,0,,Ability:\N Flawless
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:49.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Why do you want photos all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.23,0:05:49.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故急に写真なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:51.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I just feel like if we don't do it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:51.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今撮っておかないと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:57.24,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,there'll be nothing left to show \Nthat we hung out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:54.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,我々がこうやって集まったという事実を残すものが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.78,0:05:57.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何もなくなるような気がしたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.65,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku, the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作　写真機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:07.31,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,And it turned out just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.27,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その通りになった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.64,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,That day became the last \Ntime that we could record
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その日が　我々の間にある
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:15.76,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,the invisible something we shared \Nbetween us in a photograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:15.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,目に見えない何かを写真に残すことができる最後の機会になった
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:22.44,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Because one of us died soon after.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:22.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三人のうち一人がその後　間もなく死んだからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:28.03,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,The lowest-ranking member would never
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.22,0:06:31.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアの本部楼閣に最下級構成員が足を踏み入れることは先ずない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.80,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,enter the Port Mafia headquarters \Nunder normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:37.30,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,No one knows what {\i0}he{\i1} wants from me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.74,0:06:37.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,呼び出した人間にどんな用事があるのか　皆目検討がつかないが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:41.26,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,but, as far as this organization is \Nconcerned, his word is absolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:41.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この組織にいる限り　彼の言葉は絶対だ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I'm Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.77,0:06:52.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田です　首領より召集命令をいただき　参上しました
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.90,0:06:52.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I am here because I received \Na summons from the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:00.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I'm Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:00.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.39,0:07:07.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Boss, it's Oda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:08.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領　織田です　入ります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:08.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:12.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ　エリスちゃん　ドレス着てよー
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:10.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Come on, Elise-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Please wear the dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.39,0:07:13.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Just for a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一瞬　ちょこっと　一秒さっと着るだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:15.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Just put it on for a quick second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Elise,0,0,0,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:17.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,嫌よ　絶対嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.07,0:07:17.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Elise,0,0,0,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:20.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いだよ　エリスちゃん　着てみて　ねえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:19.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Come on, Elise-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Please try it on, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:22.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I put a lot of thought into picking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.30,0:07:22.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私が丹誠込めて選んだのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Look at these crimson frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.91,0:07:27.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ご覧よ　この深紅の襞　まるで葩のようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,They're like flower petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:28.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll look great in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対似合うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:31.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Elise,0,0,0,,I don't dislike pretty clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:31.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,綺麗な洋服は嫌じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:33.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Elise,0,0,0,,But I hate your desperation, Rintaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:33.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,リンタロウのその必死さが嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:37.55,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領　ご指示に従い　参上しました
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:34.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I came under your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,So, Oda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.55,0:07:52.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,却説　織田君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:53.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yes, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:53.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:56.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,You did not see anything, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.65,0:07:56.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は何も見ていない　いいね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yes, I did not see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,はい　何も見ていません
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:01.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You made time for someone like me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:05.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,首領は幼女の着替えに忙しい中　俺のような者の為に時間を割いてくれました
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:05.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,even though you were busy getting a \Nyoung girl to change her clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:07.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Why did you call me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.47,0:08:07.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　お呼び出しの理由は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:08.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.57,0:08:12.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:15.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まあいい　君を呼んだのは他でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I called you here for one \Nreason and one reason alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I need you to find someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人探しを頼みたいのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,人探し？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Find someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.05,0:08:21.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のような一介の構成員にですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:21.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You're asking me, an ordinary member?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:24.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I've heard good things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:24.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君の評判は聞いている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.17,0:08:27.18,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の仕事は是非君に頼みたい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:27.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I want to ask you specifically \Nto carry out this job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:32.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,The missing person is Sakaguchi Ango-kun,\N an intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:32.68,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,行方不明になったのは　情報員の坂口安吾君だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:37.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Ango-kun went missing last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:39.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾君が消息を絶ったのは昨日の夜　自宅に戻っていないようだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,He never got home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,He may have chosen to vanish \Nof his own free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:45.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自ら姿を消したのか　或いは何者かに拐かされたのかはまだわかっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:45.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,or he may have been abducted. \NWe do not know which is the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:50.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,As you well know, Ango-kun is a \NPort Mafia intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.22,0:08:50.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,知っての通り　安吾君はポートマフィアの情報員だ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.26,0:08:52.14,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の頭の中には
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:53.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,His head is full of secrets \Nthat would be enough
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:56.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,他の組織に売れば我々を潰せるほどの秘密が詰まっている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,to crush us if he were to sell \Nthem to other organizations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:59.08,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただし
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Even if that were not the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:04.49,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがなかったとしても　安吾君は優秀で大事な私の部下だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:04.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Ango-kun is a competent and \Nimportant staff member to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何かあったのなら扶けたい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I want to help him if \Nsomething has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,This is the Silver Oracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「銀の託宣」だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていくがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:13.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Show this to anyone in the organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:16.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これを見せれば組織内では何かと便宜が図られるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,and you'll receive some form of assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,You can even order executives around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,幹部でも顎で使える
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:23.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I've heard that you have personal relations \Nwith an executive named Dazai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:23.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は幹部の太宰君とは個人的に付き合いがあるそうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:27.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,A friendship that surpasses \Nhierarchical bounds, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.27,0:09:27.11,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,立場を超えた友情というわけだ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼の実力は飛び抜けている
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,His capabilities are astounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.66,0:09:32.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,In four, five years,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:35.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あと四五年もすれば　私を殺して首領の椅子に座っているだろうね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:35.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll have killed me \Nto sit on the throne himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:42.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Oda-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.16,0:09:43.00,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:44.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yes, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:44.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:50.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Rumors have it that you've never killed \Nanyone with that gun of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:50.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君は肩から提げているその銃で人を殺したことが一度もないという噂だが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:51.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故かね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:51.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:56.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Are you commanding me as the leader \Nof our organization to respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:56.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その質問は組織の長としての命令ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:59.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,No, it's a personal question. \NJust simple curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　私個人が発した単純な興味だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Then I prefer not to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:02.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,では　答えたくありません
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:07.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いいだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:08.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,行きたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.41,0:10:12.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Ougai,0,0,0,,I await good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:12.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,よい報告を期待しているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:20.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,市警に連絡が行かぬように手を回せ　それから掃除屋を呼べ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:20.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Ensure that the city police \Ndo not hear of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Call the cleaners, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:21.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,死体を運ばせる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:21.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,They need to transport the bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:25.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼ら三人に家族がいたか調べよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:25.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Find out if these three have families.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,If they do, I'll contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:29.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もしいれば　家族には私から連絡する
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Also, an executive will be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.74,0:10:32.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それから　間もなく幹部のお着きになる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.72,0:10:34.82,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おはよう　皆さん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.06,0:10:39.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっと待ってねー　今この難関面をクリアするところだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.10,0:10:36.33,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hang on just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.03,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm about to clear this difficult level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:41.30,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oh, crap! He's ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:41.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああまずい　抜かれた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.30,0:10:42.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Take this attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,食らえ爆撃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:43.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,避けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.05,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Damn, he dodged it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰殿　ご足労　恐縮です
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:46.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Dazai-dono, thank you for taking \Nthe trouble to come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:47.40,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,くっそー　避ける？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:49.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Our armory guards were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:48.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,武器庫警備の者が討たれました
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:53.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアの武器庫を狙うなんて　命知らずは久しぶりだねー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:50.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we last
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0,0,0,,had anyone reckless enough to \Ntarget a Port Mafia armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:57.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Each died on the spot after being hit with\Nbetween ten and twenty 9mm rounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.28,0:10:57.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,各９ミリを１０発から２０発受けて即死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Firearms were taken from the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:11:00.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その後　武器庫から銃火器が盗まれました
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.60,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Then I'll go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ見てみるよ　これお願い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.60,0:11:02.77,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Take care of this, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:05.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:07.44,Stray Dogs - Top,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't know what to do right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:07.37,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,急に渡されても…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:09.87,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This many rounds that went \Nclean through the bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.37,0:11:11.96,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この弾痕の数で貫通ってことは　近距離から短機関銃か
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:10.52,Stray Dogs - Top,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Wh-Which buttons do I press?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:11.93,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That means a sub-machine gun \Nwas used at close range.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:13.19,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなゲームが初めてです　やったことない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.32,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The assailants were pretty skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.89,0:11:14.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,かなりの手際だ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:16.19,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm getting my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:16.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,期待させてくれるね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Do we have surveillance \Nfootage of the warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:18.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,倉庫の監視映像はある？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.73,0:11:21.11,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,いかん　異能力を発揮しそうになった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:23.39,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They just look like \Nvagrants at first glance,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:25.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,パッと見たところはただの放浪者だけど　相当訓練された兵だね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.71,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,but they must be well-trained soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:26.11,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,0,,くっそー
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それぞれが死角を消すように移動してる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:29.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They are careful about covering \Neach others' blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:31.88,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Still, why take on this appearance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:31.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしこの恰好は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まずい　すこぶるまずい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.97,0:11:36.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hirotsu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.13,0:11:36.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,広津さん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:38.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,I have no excuse to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:38.46,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,面目次第も御座いません
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:41.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,If you give me another \Nchance, I will surely—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もう一度機会をいただければ必ずや…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.94,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Do you recognize this gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この銃わかる？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.33,0:11:46.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,It's an old model.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:48.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,古い型式ですな　私より年上でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.01,0:11:47.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,It's older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:52.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく「灰色の幽霊」　欧州の旧式拳銃です
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:52.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,I think it's a Graugeist. \NAn old European pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.69,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I saw this gun last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.46,0:11:56.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私この銃　昨夜見たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:07.46,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That means they attacked me right \Nbefore they hit the armory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:07.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ということは　武器庫の襲撃者はその直前に私達を襲ったことになる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.23,0:12:10.10,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It must've been a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.17,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならあれは陽動か
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This is interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:13.63,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これは面白い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:17.54,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They're a far more interesting \Nbunch than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:17.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,予想するよりずっと愉快な連中だよ　こいつらは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:24.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Hirotsu-san, they hit one of the \NPort Mafia's best storage units.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:24.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,広津さん　今回奴らが襲ったのはポートマフィア最高保管庫の一つだった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.36,0:12:27.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,They used the official passcode to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.66,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そこに正規の暗証番号で侵入している
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,番号は準幹部級の人間しか知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.75,0:12:30.87,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's only known to members who \Nare sub-executives and higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.83,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Could it mean that we have a traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか　マフィアの中に裏切り者が…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:37.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Hirotsu,0,0,0,,Don't we know who's behind these attacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.45,0:12:37.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この組織の正体　わからぬのですか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.54,0:12:42.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,うちの部下が昨日の捕虜を拷問して情報を吐かせようとしたのだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:42.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,My subordinates tortured a hostage \Nfrom yesterday to make him talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:47.80,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,but he seized an opportunity to kill himself \Nusing a suicide pill hidden in his back tooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:47.98,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一瞬の隙をついて奥歯に仕込んだ毒を呷って自害したのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:50.30,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But we did manage to learn one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ一つ聞き出せた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The organization's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の組織の名前は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.00,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.96,0:12:57.00,sign_18557_275_Episode_13___The,Sign 1254,0,0,0,,Episode 13 \N The Dark Age
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.72,0:12:55.86,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミミック
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾は宿泊亭住まいか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,So Ango lives in a hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:30.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,坂口安吾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:30.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Sakaguchi Ango...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:33.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ポートマフィアの情報員
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:33.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,An intelligence officer with the Port Mafia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,インテリでミステリアスな男
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:37.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,A mysterious intellectual,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:41.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,no one knew who you really were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:41.37,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　誰も君の正体を知らない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:46.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.66,0:13:46.90,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わからん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,通気孔か
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:54.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,A ventilation shaft?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,狙撃手か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,A sniper, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰か
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.35,0:14:32.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.61,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,珍しいね　織田作から電話なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.64,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That's rare, getting a call from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:37.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,狙撃された　安吾の部屋だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.65,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,I was targeted by a sniper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:37.93,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,In Ango's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今狙撃手を追ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.25,0:14:39.92,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,I'm going after the sniper now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:42.39,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He's firing from a building across \Nthe Secondhand Books Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,古書通りの向かいにある楼閣が狙撃点だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:44.93,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げ道を塞げってことだね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:45.21,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So you want me to cut his escape route off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.05,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,I have the Silver Oracle on hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:48.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,今手元に「銀の託宣」がある　必要なら…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:48.92,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,If you need me to, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:49.91,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,止せったら
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.92,0:14:50.02,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oh, there's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私が行くまで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.71,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard\N until I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり無理はするなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:03.41,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,動くな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:03.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:06.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げずに待ち伏せ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:06.69,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He was waiting for me \Ninstead of trying to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.58,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,狙いはこの金庫か
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.59,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He must be after this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:15.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作　屈め
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.07,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku, duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:30.53,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君はまったく困った男だな　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.64,0:15:30.54,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're quite the troublemaker, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:37.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君がその気になれば　こいつらなんか一呼吸の間に殺せるだろうに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:37.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You could have easily killed these \Nguys in an instant, if you wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:44.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の異能力「天衣無縫」は五六秒先の未来を予見することができる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:41.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,My ability, Flawless,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.52,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,allows me to see five, six \Nseconds into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,殺したのか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You killed them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:53.05,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Not like we would've gotten any \Ninformation if we'd taken them hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:53.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,生捕りにしても　情報は引き出せないからね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:58.24,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何しろ奥歯に仕込んだ毒薬の味が大好きな連中なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.37,0:15:58.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,After all, they love the \Ntaste of their poison pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:03.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,わかってるよ　そういう意味で云ったんじゃないんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:00.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.67,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That's not why you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.51,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,けどね　相手は戦闘の専門家だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.29,0:16:07.57,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But they are trained combat professionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:10.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら君でも殺さないなんて無理だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:10.55,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Even you would've been unable \Nto avoid killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.07,0:16:14.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ　お前が来なければ死んでいた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:14.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah, I would've ended up \Ndead if you hadn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作之助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.33,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oda Sakunosuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:22.34,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何があろうと絶対に人を殺さないと云う信条を持つ奇妙なポートマフィア
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:20.52,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,A curious Port Mafia member \Nwho refuses to kill anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.29,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,no matter what the circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.87,0:16:28.74,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その面倒な信念の所為で　組織内では使い走りのように扱われる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.90,0:16:25.30,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Because of that troublesome creed,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:28.81,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,you're being used as an errand \Nboy by the organization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:31.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あれだけの腕を持ちながら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.15,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,despite your considerable capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:35.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,その手の苦情はもう何万回も承ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:35.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,I've heard that complaint a million times.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,More importantly, about this attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それよりこの襲撃だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:40.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一体何者なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.09,0:16:42.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつの腰を見てみるといい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:42.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Look at his waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.69,0:16:44.96,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He's slinging an old pistol, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,旧式拳銃を提げているだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.49,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's called a Graugeist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.17,0:16:47.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつは「灰色の幽霊」と云うらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:52.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,古い欧州の拳銃で　連射性と精度がお粗末だから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:49.77,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Given that it's an old European pistol,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:52.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,it has low firing rate and accuracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.84,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この狭い路地では威嚇くらいしか使い道はない
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.93,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,So it'd only serve to fire warning \Nshots in a narrow alley like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:17:01.62,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,恐らく　その拳銃は彼らにとって　徴章のようなものなのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.31,0:17:01.59,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That pistol probably serves \Nas their emblem of some sort,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:05.36,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,to indicate who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:05.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,自分達が何者か示す為の
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:06.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何者なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:07.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,And who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:08.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミミック
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.66,0:17:08.78,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Mimic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:09.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Mimic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:09.89,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ミミック？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:12.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,詳しいことは調査中だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.18,0:17:12.76,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'm still investigating the specifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:16.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　安吾の部屋に狙撃銃を向けていた線から
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But maybe we'll find something \Nout from the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.23,0:17:18.35,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何かわかるかもしれないね
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:18.29,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,that they had a sniper watching Ango's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.79,0:17:21.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,They wanted to retrieve this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この金庫を取り戻す為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.10,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,金庫？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:22.10,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,A safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:24.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,It was in Ango's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:23.99,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾の部屋にあった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.22,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　鍵がなくて開かない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,But there was no key, and I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:28.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ　そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:29.00,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.85,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どれどれ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.27,0:17:32.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,貸して
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.79,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Let me try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.72,0:17:39.52,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Opened it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.52,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,開いた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.65,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He's sure clever with his hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.65,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,器用な奴だ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:45.40,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:45.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:47.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:50.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故だ　お前　先刻この銃は徽章だと云ったよな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:50.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You said this gun was their emblem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:53.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,A sign of who they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.04,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,連中が何者か示す為の
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,If Ango has one, it means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:55.83,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それを安吾が持ってるってことは…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:58.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけでは何とも云えない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.18,0:17:58.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,This alone is inconclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.79,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Ango may have taken this gun from them,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.80,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾がこの銃を連中から奪ったのかもしれないし
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:07.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,or they may have planted \Nthis to implicate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:07.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,或いは連中が誰かを陥れる偽装証拠としたかったのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:11.44,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,お前の云う通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.36,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど　織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:13.35,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But, Odasaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,一つ気づいたことを教えるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:16.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I'll tell you one thing I've noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:21.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,昨日酒場で飲んでいた時　安吾は取引の帰りだと云ったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.69,0:18:18.90,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Yesterday, when we were drinking at the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:21.02,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Ango said he was on his way \Nback from a deal, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.17,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,That's probably a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:23.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あれは多分嘘だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:24.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.10,0:18:26.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾の鞄を見たろ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.49,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You saw his bag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.06,0:18:29.80,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,From top to bottom, it had \Ncigarettes, a folding umbrella,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:32.75,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,上から煙草　携帯雨傘　写真機と戦利品の骨董時計が詰まっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:32.70,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,a camera, and his prize, the antique watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:37.20,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,携帯雨傘は使用されて　拭き布に巻かれていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:37.22,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The umbrella had been used, \Nand it was wrapped in cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:40.78,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして出張先の東京は雨だった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:40.81,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And his work trip was to Tokyo, \Nwhere it had rained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:45.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,雨が降って傘が濡れていた　何の不都合がある
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:43.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,So his umbrella was wet because \Nit was raining where he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.67,0:18:45.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,What's odd about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:49.32,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾は自前の車で取引現場に向かった筈だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:49.38,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Ango supposedly went there in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:52.23,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ではあの傘はいつ使われたのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:52.28,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,When did he use the umbrella, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.61,0:18:54.48,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,取引の前じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:54.36,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It wasn't before the deal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.48,0:18:57.42,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,傘は時計の上に置かれていたからね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:57.29,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,because the umbrella was \Non top of the clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.29,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そして後でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:59.12,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And it wasn't after the deal, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.29,0:19:00.02,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,何故だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:04.69,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,The umbrella was wet enough that it wasn't \Nused for a mere two or three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:04.59,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,あの傘の濡れ方は二三分使われた感じじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.39,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,たっぷり三十分は雨に打たれてた筈だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.39,0:19:08.42,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It must've been used in the rain \Nfor a good thirty minutes or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:14.03,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけ雨の中にいたにしては　安吾の靴もズボンの裾も乾いていた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:11.11,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But despite supposedly being \Nin the rain for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:14.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,his shoes and pants were dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,取引が八時で　我々が会ったのが十時
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:17.91,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,If his deal was at eight and \Nwe met at the bar at ten,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:22.09,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,取引の後　二時間では乾くのに時間が足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:22.20,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,two hours weren't enough for \Nhis shoes and pants to dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:24.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,着替えを持っていたのかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:24.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Maybe he changed clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:28.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,酒場からの帰りに　安吾の車に便乗したが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:26.06,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He drove me home in his car,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:30.02,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,but I didn't see any change \Nof clothes or shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:30.01,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,靴も着替えもなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:35.47,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の予想では　安吾は取引には行かず　雨の中誰かに会い
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:34.16,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I think Ango didn't go to a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.16,0:19:35.48,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He met someone in the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:40.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,三十分くらい会話をしてから　残りの時間を潰して帰ってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:38.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,spoke to them for about thirty minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:40.73,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,and then killed some time \Nbefore coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.27,0:19:47.64,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾のような情報員は　しばしば雨の降る路上を密会の場所に選ぶことがある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.76,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Intelligence officers like \NAngo sometimes choose
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:47.66,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,a rainy road for their secret meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.25,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It's more secure than an indoor \Nspace for classified talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:50.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,室内より密談に向いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:53.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Ango is the Port Mafia's \Nclassified intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:53.76,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾はポートマフィアの秘密情報員だ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:57.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Of course he'd have one or two meetings \Nhe couldn't tell anyone about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:57.07,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,誰にも明かせぬ密会の一つや二つあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:19:59.26,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Then he could've just said \Nthat he couldn't tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.41,0:19:59.25,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,ならば一言云えばいい
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:05.32,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,If he had, both you and I wouldn't \Nhave asked any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.62,0:20:00.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「云えない」と
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.33,0:20:05.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば私も織田作も　それ以上は聞かない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.27,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.29,Stray Dogs - Italics,Oda,0,0,0,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.28,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにその通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:16.30,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なのに　アリバイまで用意して　密会を隠したかった理由はなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.75,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And yet, he even made up an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:16.23,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,What was the reason that he had to go \Nto such lengths to hide that meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:26.73,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おやおや　大した精神力だね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:26.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Well, you have commendable spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,実際のところ私は　君達を敬畏しているのだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:31.68,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, \NI hold you all in awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:35.99,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,No other organization has managed \Nto face the Port Mafia head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.99,0:20:35.95,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,これほど正面からポートマフィアにぶつかってくる組織はなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:37.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰　よせっ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.99,0:20:36.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.97,0:20:37.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.97,0:20:45.36,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I hope you can see the joy in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:45.26,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,私の目の中の歓喜が君にも見えることを願うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:52.57,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,君がほんの少し指を曲げるだけで　私が最も待ち焦がれたものが訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:49.04,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,With just a slight press of your finger,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.56,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,you can give me what I desire most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:56.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,My only fear is that \Nyou'll miss your target.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:56.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一の恐れは　君が狙いを外すことだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:58.38,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,But you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:21:00.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,だができるさ　君は狙撃手だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.09,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,You're a sniper, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.92,0:21:01.72,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.81,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,どの道　君は殺される
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.86,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Either way, you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.31,0:21:07.31,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,なら　最後に敵幹部を葬ってみせろ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:07.32,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,At least try to kill one of the \Nenemy executives before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.56,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,止めろ　太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Stop it, Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.38,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,頼むよ　私を一緒に連れて行ってくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.80,0:21:12.37,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Please, take me with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:16.79,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,この酸化する世界の夢から醒めさせてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.70,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Wake me from this oxidizing \Nworld of a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:17.45,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.06,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,悪いね　吃驚させて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.07,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Sorry to shock you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:34.60,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,迫真の演技だったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.15,0:21:34.59,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,It was great acting, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.21,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,演技？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:36.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Acting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.51,0:21:38.84,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I knew he'd miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.05,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,彼が外すことはわかっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:42.82,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,狙撃銃の跡は左頬についていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.76,0:21:42.80,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,His left cheek had the imprint \Nfrom the sniper's rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:44.77,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり彼は左利きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.77,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,In other words, he is left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:50.67,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,利き腕ではない右手のうえ　まともに立てないほどふらついた状態で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:47.58,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He was using his non-dominant right hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:50.74,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,and he was so unsteady that \Nhe could barely stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:56.54,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,おまけにあの旧式拳銃では　銃口を額につけない限り中たらないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.02,0:21:53.39,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,And with that old pistol?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:56.60,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have succeeded unless he had the \Ngun pressed up right against my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:22:03.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,会話で時間を稼いで彼の腕が疲れれば　あとは織田作が何とかしてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:22:03.21,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,I knew you'd do something if I bought enough \Ntime with talk to tire his arm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.13,0:22:04.70,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,やめろ　太宰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:04.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Just stop, Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:05.71,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もういい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.72,0:22:05.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:09.33,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,織田作
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:09.38,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Odasaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.74,0:22:16.13,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,安吾を頼む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:16.18,Stray Dogs - Default,D,0,0,0,,Please find Ango.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.18,0:22:20.42,TEXT-JP(UP)-ja,,0,0,51,,{\fs30}ああ　わかってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.22,0:22:20.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Oda,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:21.15,sign_32086_429_Next_Time__Episo,Sign 2219,0,0,0,,Next Time: Episode 14 \N Nowhere to Return
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:43.88,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,「灰色の幽霊」　あの銃は符牒です
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:47.16,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,撃鉄に特別な彫り込みがしてあって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.16,0:23:50.12,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,それがミミックの一員であることを証明します
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:53.94,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,僕もあの銃をもらい受けるのに一年かかりました
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:57.15,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,坂口安吾　お前は…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:24:01.87,TEXT-JP-ja,,0,0,0,,もし許されるなら　三人でもう一度飲みたかった
